            <p>
                Formerly known as College of Pedagogy BD (from 1976 to 2009), Thu Dau Mot University was founded by virtue of Prime Minister’s Decision No. 900/QĐ/TTg  dated June 24th, 2009. The Mission of the school is to train high quality human resources serve socio-economic development of Binh Duong Province, Southeast provinces, the Southern Key Economic Zone and country; scientific research, application and transfer of science and technology, providing products and services to market.
            </p>
            <p>
                In 2015, the scientific staff of TDMU has 1 Professor, 8 Associate Professors Doctor, 56 doctoral, 454 masters, 40 faculty members and non-teaching staffs are domestic and international research students. In parallel with the construction of scientific regular lecturers, the university also enlist the support of professionally qualified faculty in the fields of National University of Ho Chi Minh City, National University of Hanoi, Pedagogy University of Ho Chi Minh City ,especially for strengths field is the social sciences and humanities.

            </p>
            <p>
                August 2015, Ministry of Education and Training allowed enrolling 5 post graduate sectors, marked an important step in the development of the school. The size of TDMU curently is 18000 students, students are learning and researching in 5 the postgraduate sectors, 22 undergraduate academic,6 masters in College in the fields of Economics, engineering, natural sciences, Social Sciences Humanities and pedagogy.
            </p>
            <p>
                Over 6 years of establishment and development, TDM university has formed a multidisciplinary institution by research-oriented. With the motto "knowledge-development-prosperity", TDM University is gradually confirmed the status of institution as training, researching scientific high quality, is represented for the strength of youth knowledge of Binh Duong Province.
            </p>
